{"ja438:0.1":"Jataka ","ja438:0.2":"Navakanipata ","ja438:0.3":"Gijjhavagga ","ja438:0.4":"12. Daddarajataka ","ja438:1.1":"“Yo te puttake akhadi, ","ja438:1.2":"dinnabhatto adusake; ","ja438:1.3":"Tasmim datham nipatehi, ","ja438:1.4":"ma te muccittha jivato”. ","ja438:2.1":"“Akinnaluddo puriso, ","ja438:2.2":"dhaticelamva makkhito; ","ja438:2.3":"Padesam tam na passami, ","ja438:2.4":"yattha datham nipataye. ","ja438:3.1":"Akatannussa posassa, ","ja438:3.2":"niccam vivaradassino; ","ja438:3.3":"Sabbance pathavim dajja, ","ja438:3.4":"neva nam abhiradhaye”. ","ja438:4.1":"“Kim nu subahu taramanarupo, ","ja438:4.2":"Paccagatosi saha manavena; ","ja438:4.3":"Kim kiccamattham idhamatthi tuyham, ","ja438:4.4":"Akkhahi me pucchito etamattham”. ","ja438:5.1":"“Yo te sakha daddaro sadhurupo, ","ja438:5.2":"Tassa vadham parisankami ajja; ","ja438:5.3":"Purisassa kammayatanani sutva, ","ja438:5.4":"Naham sukhim daddaram ajja manne”. ","ja438:6.1":"“Kanissa kammayatanani assu, ","ja438:6.2":"Purisassa vuttisamodhanataya; ","ja438:6.3":"Kam va patinnam purisassa sutva, ","ja438:6.4":"Parisankasi daddaram manavena”. ","ja438:7.1":"“Cinna kalinga carita vanijja, ","ja438:7.2":"Vettacaro sankupathopi cinno; ","ja438:7.3":"Natehi cinnam saha vakurehi, ","ja438:7.4":"Dandena yuddhampi samajjamajjhe. ","ja438:8.1":"Baddha kulika mitamalhakena, ","ja438:8.2":"Akkha jita samyamo abbhatito; ","ja438:8.3":"Abbahitam pubbakam addharattam, ","ja438:8.4":"Hattha daddha pindapatiggahena. ","ja438:9.1":"Tanissa kammayatanani assu, ","ja438:9.2":"Purisassa vuttisamodhanataya; ","ja438:9.3":"Yatha ayam dissati lomapindo, ","ja438:9.4":"Gavo hata kim pana daddarassa”ti. ","ja438:10.1":"Daddarajatakam dvadasamam. ","ja438:11.1":"Navakanipatam nitthitam. ","ja438:12.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja438:13.1":"Varagijjha samajjana hamsavaro, ","ja438:13.2":"Nidhisavhaya harita pataliko; ","ja438:13.3":"Ajaramara dhanka titikkha kuto, ","ja438:13.4":"Atha dvadasa pekkhana daddaribhiti. "}